{"tid":863041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"be aware of 激進五毛","createTime":"2018-10-15T10:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T10:49:16.000Z","uid":142903,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b44bf7dde3cbe255b4260227cba42e5d485111a7","tid":863041,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"大家佔領過都知呢個香港大致分類人<br />\n<br />\n五毛 港豬 泛民 本土 港獨<br />\n<br />\n要一樣野成功要拎一半人以上認同唔反對<br />\n<br />\n而家本土港獨明顯知道呢點所以有時同泛民磨擦都會息事寧人<br />\n<br />\n呀你老味而家五毛做分身將個光譜拉到<br />\n<br />\n五毛 港豬 泛民 本土 港獨 唔知為乜勇武<br />\n<br />\n不斷拎本土港獨之旗打泛民港豬<br />\n<br />\n屌票屌支持<br />\n<br />\n搞到自己神憎鬼厭<br />\n<br />\n實際就係想本土港獨更加不得人心<br />\n<br />\n我會叫呢班做激進五毛<br />\n<br />\n呢班人目的唔係真勇武<br />\n<br />\n而係散擋是但一班係鬼呢個概念<br />\n<br />\n尋日搶咪單野大家都知柒柒地<br />\n<br />\n呢班激進五毛係要扮晒勇武咁<br />\n<br />\n實際上美領事館都冇去<br />\n<br />\n含撚啦"},{"pid":"ca74ac36da040e1b26be3907bb095877feef8d9a","tid":863041,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00617167832c2d84903aa8b0570d018317e9a1f","tid":863041,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"beware of goodest english"},{"pid":"42c379b9ef5c27bb09c2d9975e2b5a3508056074","tid":863041,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e00617167832c2d84903aa8b0570d018317e9a1f","tid":863041,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"beware of goodest english"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:29:13.000Z","msg":"i go to school by bus"},{"pid":"332b599808db802d54da3da1885b2fcd6d4c56bf","tid":863041,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}